eed demanding results our company  our brands  leadership  investor relations  newsroom  careers  contact us industry links  privacy policy scroll to top our company  omnimax international inc  building products our companyyou are here home  our companyour company omnimax international inc is a leading manufacturer of building and transportation products we offer  products with endless possibilities watch how our industry leading brands build on one another omnimax international inc is an international building products company manufacturing aluminum steel vinyl and copper products the company was formed in  to acquire the fabricated products business of alumax inc an integrated aluminum producer core products include specialty coated coils metal wall and roof systems metal and vinyl rain carrying systems soffit and fascia systems roofing accessories aluminum and vinyl windows and doors patio products aluminum recreational vehicle doors windows and sidewalls and aluminum bath and shower enclosures products are then represented in the market by multiple brands such as amerimax and fabral the strength of the business model is the supply of fabricated components to original equipment manufacturers oem’s distributors contractors and home centers throughout north america and western europe omnimax has grown both organically and through a number of strategic acquisitions to become one of the largest suppliers of specialty coated aluminum coil building materials and rv sidewalls in the us and western europe omnimax international inc is a wholly owned subsidiary of omnimax holdings inc explore our brands by the markets we service architectural  commercial residential post frame  agricultural recreational vehicles  transportation our company  our brands  leadership  investor relations  newsroom  careers  contact us industry links  privacy policy scroll to top euramax holdings inc private company information  bloomberg july    pm et building products company overview of euramax holdings inc snapshot people company overview euramax holdings inc produces and sells residential and commercial building materials and recreational vehicle rv exterior components primarily in north america and europe the company operates through four segments us residential products us commercial products european roll coated aluminum and european engineered products the us residential products segment offers residential roof drainage products including preformed gutters downspouts elbows soffits drip edges fascias flashings snow guards and related accessories which are primarily used for the repair replacement or enhancement of residential roof drainage systems and vinyl replacement windows and aluminum  euramax holdings inc produces and sells residential and commercial building materials and recreational vehicle rv exterior components primarily in north america and europe the company operates through four segments us residential products us commercial products european roll coated aluminum and european engineered products the us residential products segment offers residential roof drainage products including preformed gutters downspouts elbows soffits drip edges fascias flashings snow guards and related accessories which are primarily used for the repair replacement or enhancement of residential roof drainage systems and vinyl replacement windows and aluminum patio and awning components to home improvement contractors the us commercial products segment provides roofing and siding panels ridge caps flashings trims soffits and other accessories as well as sidewall components sidings and other exterior components for use in the construction of various small scale commercial agricultural and industrial building types the european roll coated aluminum segment produces specialty coated coil and processes into specialty coated sheets and panels this segment’s specialty coated metal products are used to manufacture rv sidewalls commercial roofing panels interior ceiling panels and liner panels for shipping containers the european engineered products segment offers residential windows doors and shower enclosures windows used in the operator compartments of heavy equipment components for automotive original equipment manufacturers and rv doors the company serves home improvement retailers industrial and architectural contractors rural contractors distributors home improvement contractors and manufactured housing producers euramax holdings inc was founded in  and is headquartered in norcross georgia detailed description  research drivesuite norcross ga united statesfounded in  employees phone  key executives for euramax holdings inc mr richard c brown chief executive officer president and director age  ms mary s cullin chief financial officer principal accounting officer senior vice president and treasurer age  mr jan timmerman president of international and managing director of international age  mr dudley rowe president of amerimax home products inc age  mr nick dowd president of fabral inc age  compensation as of fiscal year  euramax holdings inc key developments euramax holdings inc q  earnings call apr   mar   euramax holdings inc q  earnings call apr   euramax holdings inc q  earnings call nov   nov   euramax holdings inc q  earnings call nov   euramax holdings inc presents at deutsche bank th annual leveraged finance conference sep aug   euramax holdings inc presents at deutsche bank th annual leveraged finance conference sep  venue the phoenician  east camelback road scottsdale az  arizona united states similar private companies by industry company name region st united door technologies inc united states  company inc united states  lumber company  lumber sales and supply centers and  truss manufacturing plant united states a  a window products inc united states a b c steel products co inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update