x louvered roof euramax coated products euramax industries fabral and global expanded metals through strategic acquisitions and dedication to superior customer satisfaction euramax has become one of north america’s largest suppliers of building products for more information visit wwweuramaxcomcontact mary cullin senior vice president chief financial officer and treasurer euramax holdings inc  research drive suite  norcross georgia   related articles other press releases by omnimax international inc omnimax holdings inc announces first quarter  investor call information may    omnimax holdings inc announces fourth quarter and full year  investor call information march    euramax holdings inc announces third quarter  investor call information november    euramax holdings inc announces second quarter  investor call information august    euramax holdings inc announces first quarter  investor call information may     other news releases in mergers and acquisitions in the last  days profile omnimax international inc   subscribe via rss  subscribe via atom  javascript norcross georgia united states   httpwwweuramaxcom contact data contact mary cullin senior vice president chief financial officer and treasurer euramax holdings inc  research drive suite  norcross georgia   media files omnimax international inc logo logo url  copy the link below formats available original medium small newswire distribution network  management home newsroom rss feeds legal contact us about us globenewswire a nasdaq company is one of the worlds largest newswire distribution networks specializing in the delivery of corporate press releases financial disclosures and multimedia content to the media investment community individual investors and the general public contact us corporate headquarters  rosecrans avenue suite  el segundo ca  phone   fax   european headquarters woolgate exchange  basinghall street london ecv ha uk phone     globenewswire inc all rights reserved   omnimax international inc